setCrewMemberStatus(CrewMember) - Method in class main.Crew
Sets a crew member's status (alive or dead) with some specified conditions:
– If health is under (or equals) 0%
– If hunger is maxed and over (or equals) 50%
– If tiredness is maxed and over (or equals) 50%
If any of these conditions are met crew member's status is set to false: dead

stealCrewItem(Crew) - Method in class main.AlienPirates
Called when alien pirates steal foodstuff or medical item from a crew
Event is set up by a random generator out of 10,
– If number is over 5 then every alien pirates steal items

If a crew member of type Terminator is present within crew members,
then aliens will not be able to steal items but the particular
member of type Terminator will get 10% damage
